---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../../site.config';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Affiliate Disclosure - ${siteConfig.name}`}
  description="How Dry Climate Beauty earns revenue through affiliate links, and why it never influences our editorial recommendations."
>
  <main class="page-content">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

      <section>
        <p>
          Dry Climate Beauty is an independent publication. We earn revenue through affiliate links, which means that when you click a product link in one of our articles and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission from the retailer. This costs you nothing extra.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
        <p>
          Affiliate commissions help fund our editorial operations, including product testing, medical review, and research. They do not influence which products we recommend, how we rate them, or what we write about them.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our editorial team selects products for review based on relevance to hard water and dry climate conditions, ingredient quality, and reader interest. Products that perform poorly in testing receive honest assessments regardless of affiliate availability.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Disclose</h2>
        <p>
          Every article that contains affiliate links includes a disclosure statement near the top of the page. This disclosure appears before you encounter any product links, so you always know before clicking.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Medical Review Independence</h2>
        <p>
          Our medical reviewer, Dr. Layla Hassan, has no financial relationship with any products featured on the site. Her review is limited to factual accuracy of health claims and is completely independent of our commercial relationships.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Questions</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or believe a recommendation may have been influenced by a commercial relationship, contact <strong>editorial@dryclimatebeauty.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }
  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
</style>